body:
Comment 5: 
Do you see the line

DEF_FUNCTION_TYPE (VOID, PLONGLONG, LONGLONG)

in gcc/config/i386/i386-builtin-types.def?  It should be right after

DEF_FUNCTION_TYPE (VOID, PINT, INT)

and right before

DEF_FUNCTION_TYPE (VOID, PULONGLONG, ULONGLONG)

It seems to be missing in the excerpt of the i386.i file above.
